@startuml
participant "OZO Platform\n(Team A)" as TeamA
participant "FHIR API" as FHIR
participant "OZO Platform\n(Team B)" as TeamB

== Thread Creation (Team A initiates) ==
TeamA -> FHIR : Create CommunicationRequest\n(status: 'active')\nrequester/sender = Practitioner A1\nextension[senderCareTeam] = CareTeam A\nrecipient = CareTeam B
FHIR -> FHIR : Create Communication\n(initial message)\nsender = Practitioner A1\nrecipient = CareTeam B
FHIR -> FHIR : Create Tasks\nfor each CareTeam B member\n(status: 'requested')
FHIR -> TeamB : Notify of new Tasks\n[Via Subscription]
TeamB -> FHIR : Fetch CommunicationRequest\nand Communication
note over TeamB : Thread appears in\nTeam B's shared inbox

== Reply from Team B ==
TeamB -> FHIR : Create Communication\nsender = Practitioner B1\nrecipient = CareTeam A\n(from extension[senderCareTeam])
FHIR -> FHIR : Create/Update Tasks\nfor CareTeam A members\n(status: 'requested')
FHIR -> FHIR : Complete Tasks\nfor other CareTeam B members
FHIR -> TeamA : Notify of new Tasks\n[Via Subscription]
TeamA -> FHIR : Fetch Communication
note over TeamA : New message in\nTeam A's shared inbox

== Follow-up from Different Team A Member ==
TeamA -> FHIR : Create Communication\nsender = Practitioner A2\n(different team member)\nrecipient = CareTeam B
FHIR -> FHIR : Create/Update Tasks\nfor CareTeam B members\n(status: 'requested')
FHIR -> FHIR : Complete Tasks\nfor other CareTeam A members
FHIR -> TeamB : Notify of new Tasks\n[Via Subscription]
TeamB -> FHIR : Fetch Communication

== Read Receipt ==
TeamB -> FHIR : Create AuditEvent\n(action: 'R')\nagent = Practitioner B1
FHIR -> FHIR : Complete Task\nfor Practitioner B1
note over FHIR : Message marked as read\nfor all CareTeam B members
FHIR -> TeamA : Notify Task update\n[Via Subscription]
note over TeamA : Message shown as\nread by Team B
@enduml
